##description: Custom GTF for the CloneTracker XP construct.
##notes: Length below (720 bp) MUST be updated to match the real construct sequence
## once you replace clonetracker_construct.fa. The exon must span 1..length.
## gene_biotype "protein_coding" so that Cell Ranger keeps the contig in the
## filtered matrix.
CloneTracker_construct	custom	exon	1	720	.	+	.	gene_id "CloneTracker"; transcript_id "CloneTracker.1"; gene_name "CloneTracker"; gene_biotype "protein_coding";
